---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <p class="font-bold text-gray-500">Last updated: May 2026</p>

      <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-black rounded-2xl p-6 brutal-shadow">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-lg">We collect information you provide directly, such as when you contact us. We also automatically collect certain information about your device, including your IP address, browser type, and operating system.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-black rounded-2xl p-6 brutal-shadow">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-lg">We use the information we collect to operate and maintain our website, respond to your comments and questions, and improve our content and user experience.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-black rounded-2xl p-6 brutal-shadow">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">3. Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-lg">We use cookies to enhance your experience. You can control cookies through your browser settings. See our <a href="/cookie-policy" class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-2 font-bold">Cookie Policy</a> for more details.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-black rounded-2xl p-6 brutal-shadow">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-lg">We may use third-party services such as analytics and advertising partners. These services may collect information about your online activities over time.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-black rounded-2xl p-6 brutal-shadow">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">5. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-lg">We implement reasonable security measures to protect your personal information. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-black rounded-2xl p-6 brutal-shadow">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">6. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-lg">Our website is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-black rounded-2xl p-6 brutal-shadow">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-lg">We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-black rounded-2xl p-6 brutal-shadow">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">8. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-lg">If you have questions about this privacy policy, please <a href="/contact" class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-2 font-bold">contact us</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
